title: Rollover on U.S. 31
maintext:
Rollover on U.S. 31
Emergency responders were called to a rollover accident along U.S. 31 near Chauvez Road at 8:52 a.m. Thursday.
Pere Marquette firefighters, law enforcement officers, the Ludington Fire Department Jaws of Life team and Life EMS personnel were called to the scene.
A male victim was reported to have minor injuries.
See the story and photos in your Thursday Ludington Daily News.
